(08:39)  Several singles associations organize dancing of various kinds. While for people in a real hurry, there's speed dating in which everyone talks to everyone else for just 5 minutes. Then at the end, they decide which of them they would like to meet again by ticking their names on a list. In complete contrast to these are the many religious associations reflecting the diversity of faith groups present in this multicultural city.
