(10:19)  Whether you enjoy taking part or just watching and listening, you can take your pick from a whole range of groups. To take just a couple of examples, there's light opera at the memorial hall in the city center or a very lively amateur theater company in the park district. In summer they give open air performances of Shakespeare plays free of charge.
